    <Folder>
      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The current military posture and activity patterns suggest a high level of operational tempo, with numerous aircraft and vessels engaged in various missions worldwide. The presence of A-10 Warthogs and F-16s in the Middle East region indicates a significant airpower commitment to Operation Epic Fury. The deployment of USNS DAHL and USNS EFFECTIVE to ports in the northeastern United States and Japan, respectively, may be related to logistics and supply chain operations. The overall assessment is that the U.S. military is maintaining a strong and active presence globally, with a focus on supporting ongoing operations and maintaining readiness for potential future conflicts.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
    </Folder>
